  "text": "A prototype of a multi-UAV network, called UAVNet, is suggested in [CITATION_1] . A framework for flying wireless mesh A network of small UAVs, wirelessly connected through IEEE 802.11g, carrying cameras and sensors in disaster management applications have been studied in [CITATION_2] . The primary goal is to have efficient cooperation among the UAVs through the network. Their proposed aerial imaging system for mission-critical situations is capable of providing services for different desired levels of detail and resolution.",
